quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,78,He est 1 qui granted vos hearing eyesight brains! Rarely est vos appreciative
  23,79,He est Unus established vos terra ac Eum vos summoned
  23,80,He est Unus controls vita decessus He est 1 qui alternates nox feria. Vos non understand
  23,81,They dictus quod their patres dictus
  23,82,They dictus Post nos abiit become dust bones nos get resurrected
  23,83,Such promises dedit nos noster parentes in the elapsus. These est non multus than tales ex preter
  23,84,"Dictus, \"To whom belongs terra everyone it si vos know"
  23,85,"They dictus, \"To DEUS. Dictus tunc vos non take heed"
  23,86,Dictus Qui est Dominus de 7 universes; Dominus major dominion
  23,87,They dictus DEUS. Dictus tunc vos non turn righteous
  23,88,Dictus In whose manus est totus sovereignty totus things He unus unus provisus help needs nullus help vos est know
  23,89,They dictus DEUS. Dictus Ubi testimentum vos iit wrong
  23,90,Nos dedit them truth dum they est liars
  23,91,DEUS NUNQUAM GENITUS EST FILIUS. Nor est ibi ever any alius deus Eum. Alias each deus declared independence his creations they competed each alius pro dominance! DEUS glorified far their claims
  23,92,Knower de totus secrets declarations; He exalted far habet partner